dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.cbe.party.prof.PartyProfile
dataStructure.description:
A match between a Party and a PartyProfileType. It is based on matching PartyDemographics and other Party characteristics, such as use of a product, with the characteristics of a PartyProfileType.

This entity is optional
